PostgreSQL dependency prefix.

Target triple: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@

Included dependency sources:
  krb5 @KRB5_VERSION@ (Linux only)
  keyutils @KEYUTILS_VERSION@ (Linux only)
  cyrus-sasl @CYRUS_SASL_VERSION@ (Linux only)
  OpenLDAP @OPENLDAP_VERSION@ (Linux only)
  json-c @JSON_C_VERSION@
  libxcrypt @LIBXCRYPT_VERSION@ (Linux only)
  libevent @LIBEVENT_VERSION@
  liburing @LIBURING_VERSION@ (Linux only)
  Linux-PAM @LINUX_PAM_VERSION@ (Linux only)
  systemd @SYSTEMD_VERSION@ SDK libsystemd (Linux only)
